OL,3,CModel railway show returns to
OL,4,CAlexandra Palace
OL,6,FModel railway enthusiasts from across
OL,7,Fthe country have gathered at Alexandra
OL,8,FPalace this weekend to celebrate the
OL,9,Fhobby.
OL,11,FThousands of miniature trains are on
OL,12,Fdisplay at The London Festival of
OL,13,FRailway Modelling - which returned to
OL,14,Fthe north London venue for it's 25th
OL,15,Ftime.
OL,17,FThe festival is one of the UK's
OL,18,Flargest and most respected model
OL,19,Frailway exhibitions.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/5
