OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1774375556
OL,3,CModel railway show returns to
OL,4,CAlexandra Palace
OL,6,FMore than 40 model railway layouts are
OL,7,Fon display, showcasing work from the
OL,8,FUK, Europe, and the US.
OL,10,FFrom classic steam railways to modern
OL,11,Fscenes, the displays filled two great
OL,12,Fhalls, with a number of layouts based
OL,13,Fon regions in the UK.
OL,15,FAlso at the event are more than 90
OL,16,Ftraders, retailers and manufacturers
OL,17,Fproviding tips and demonstrations for
OL,18,Fvisitors.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/5
