PN,40804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1774375556
OL,3,CModel railway show returns to
OL,4,CAlexandra Palace
OL,6,F"From the world's first underground
OL,7,Fnetwork to the millions of journeys
OL,8,Fmade every single day, railways have
OL,9,Fbeen a huge part of the capital for
OL,10,Fmore than 160 years.
OL,12,F"So, being here at the iconic
OL,13,FAlexandra Palace for our 25th
OL,14,Fanniversary, completely immersed in
OL,15,Fthe world of railways, feels like the
OL,16,Fperfect way to bring the hobby to life
OL,17,Fover the weekend."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/5
